OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day with some good spells
OL,6,Fof sunshine. Cloudier in the morning,
OL,7,Fespecially in the north around Angus,
OL,8,Fwith a cloudier period possible around
OL,9,Fthe middle of the day also.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight. Some prolonged
OL,13,Fspells of evening sunshine leading to
OL,14,Fsome clear spells overnight meaning it
OL,15,Fmight feel chilly compared to recent
OL,16,Fweeks.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
