OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FDry with lengthy bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells and feeling warmer again.
OL,7,FSunshine turning hazy later as high
OL,8,Fcloud spreads southeast. Cloudier in
OL,9,Fthe evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FIt
OL,12,Fwill be a dry few days with variable
OL,13,Fcloud and some sunny spells. Mainly
OL,14,Flight winds, and turning warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
